        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "If we open the wall and find active mold growth, we'll let you know immediately. Minor surface mold on drywall we're already replacing isn't typically a separate issue ‚Äî removing the compromised material handles it. For significant mold infestations, we'll recommend a mold remediation specialist before we do our structural repairs."
      }
    }
  ]
